SMOKED SHORT RIBS 🍖
EAT or PASS? Tag a friend to eat this with
➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖
FOLLOW ➡️ @meat_with .
➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖
.
There is no limit to tenderness!!! thanks for sharing it with us 📹  @plazoo_bbq using 🍖
.
my method step by step:
Low and slow smoked inside my BGE till internal temp 75C/167F. Than I wrapped it in a butcher paper till internal temp 95C/203F. I use my @meatermade ThermoMEATER BLOCK (LINK IN BIO) Two more hours rest inside a thermo box. It is important to moisten the meat with a spritz or brush with any liquid Every half hour and before wrap (apple vinegar, Beer, natural juice, wine or just water with spices).

.
.
.
.

Prime Tomahawk (Ribeye) 3.7 Pound all that marble and bone is nothing but dryaged flavor. It's probably Hand Of the Meat Gods. I’m totally mouth watering 🤤👅🤤

3/4 cup Paprika

2 tbsp granulated garlic

Direct fire for the outside fat. 3 minutes rest before cutting.  WOW!
